<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Confirmation - Prestigio Motors</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
            color: #d4af37;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #d4af37;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.5);
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #2c2c2c;
        }
        .appointment-details {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f9f9f9 0%, #f0f0f0 100%);
            border-left: 4px solid #d4af37;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .appointment-details h3 {
            color: #d4af37;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #d4af37;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 12px 0;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #333;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .vehicle-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2a2a2a 100%);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #d4af37;
        }
        .vehicle-section h3 {
            color: #d4af37;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #d4af37;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .vehicle-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .vehicle-detail {
            background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border-left: 3px solid #d4af37;
        }
        .vehicle-detail-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #d4af37;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .vehicle-detail-value {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .total-price {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #d4af37;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background: #e8f4f8;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .next-steps h3 {
            color: #2196F3;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            color: #d4af37;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 3px solid #d4af37;
        }
        .contact-info {
            margin: 20px 0;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            color: #d4af37;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .vehicle-details {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: left;
            }
            .detail-value {
                text-align: left;
                margin-top: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>PRESTIGIO MOTORS</h1>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">LUXURY AUTOMOTIVE EXCELLENCE</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Dear {{customerName}},
            </div>

            <p>Thank you for choosing Prestigio Motors. We are delighted to confirm your appointment with our luxury automotive specialists.</p>

            <div class="appointment-details">
                <h3>ðŸ“… Appointment Details</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Service:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{service}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{date}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Time:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{time}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Reference ID:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">#{{orderId}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            {{#if vehicleDetails}}
            <div class="vehicle-section">
                <h3>ðŸš— Vehicle Configuration</h3>
                <div class="vehicle-details">
                    <div class="vehicle-detail">
                        <div class="vehicle-detail-label">Vehicle</div>
                        <div class="vehicle-detail-value">{{vehicleDetails.carName}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{#if vehicleDetails.options.color}}
                    <div class="vehicle-detail">
                        <div class="vehicle-detail-label">Color</div>
                        <div class="vehicle-detail-value">{{vehicleDetails.options.color}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if vehicleDetails.options.finish}}
                    <div class="vehicle-detail">
                        <div class="vehicle-detail-label">Finish</div>
                        <div class="vehicle-detail-value">{{vehicleDetails.options.finish}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if vehicleDetails.options.wheels}}
                    <div class="vehicle-detail">
                        <div class="vehicle-detail-label">Wheels</div>
                        <div class="vehicle-detail-value">{{vehicleDetails.options.wheels}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if vehicleDetails.options.interior}}
                    <div class="vehicle-detail">
                        <div class="vehicle-detail-label">Interior</div>
                        <div class="vehicle-detail-value">{{vehicleDetails.options.interior}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    {{#if vehicleDetails.options.performance}}
                    <div class="vehicle-detail">
                        <div class="vehicle-detail-label">Performance</div>
                        <div class="vehicle-detail-value">{{vehicleDetails.options.performance}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
                {{#if vehicleDetails.totalPrice}}
                <div class="total-price">
                    Total Configuration: ${{vehicleDetails.totalPrice}}
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>What's Next?</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Our luxury automotive specialist will contact you within 24 hours to confirm your appointment</li>
                    <li>Please arrive 15 minutes early to complete any necessary paperwork</li>
                    <li>Bring a valid driver's license if you're planning a test drive</li>
                    <li>Feel free to contact us if you need to reschedule or have any questions</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>We look forward to providing you with an exceptional luxury automotive experience at Prestigio Motors.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
                Warm regards,<br>
                <strong>The Prestigio Motors Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="contact-info">
                <strong>PRESTIGIO MOTORS</strong><br>
                Sixth District, Al Obour City<br>
                Phone: +2 01098613073<br>
                Email: prestegioautomobiles@gmail.com
            </div>
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Facebook</a> |
                <a href="#">Instagram</a> |
                <a href="#">Twitter</a> |
                <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
                Â© 2025 Prestigio Motors. All rights reserved.<br>
                This email was sent regarding your appointment request.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 